Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.96,0:00:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.58,0:00:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.01,0:01:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}HEroAP Presents
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.01,0:01:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Amber Reminiscence
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.97,0:01:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Hikaru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.31,0:01:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I know this isn't the right time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.94,0:01:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But, we're in this weird place...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And we may be stuck here... So...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.23,0:01:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.57,0:01:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But, to hug you like that out of nowhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.53,0:01:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You really didn't need that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.41,0:02:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.12,0:02:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,"I didn't need that...?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.42,0:02:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.38,0:02:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.61,0:02:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.24,0:02:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you and Miyuki-chan related?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my younger sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.95,0:02:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.08,0:02:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really mean that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.33,0:02:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you only see her as your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.54,0:02:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.97,0:03:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be gentle with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.39,0:03:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,T-That's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.81,0:03:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my... first kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan, you're already...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.22,0:04:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't say that, this is embarrassing enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.46,0:04:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hikaru-san, don't... do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:05:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels... weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go easy on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.91,0:05:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.67,0:05:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all the way in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Just tell me if it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I hurting you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This position's really embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.32,0:06:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.11,0:06:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.71,0:07:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That looks like...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Something from a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought that I'd be with you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.95,0:07:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you... regret doing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.49,0:07:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I... do love you, Hikaru-san. But I also don't\Nthink I should have you to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,For you to be my first... That\Nalone makes me very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I really mean that... so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.69,0:08:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe... we should go back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Amaterasu told me that we can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we're all here, we'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what's happened, or what\Npainful experiences I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Your warmth has always been there to comfort me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really have to leave us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.11,0:09:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... We can't intrude on your goodwill,\Nand we're already indebted to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.41,0:09:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really are Izanami's kyuseishuu\Nthat was sent to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.92,0:09:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm simply a normal\Nperson with a normal lineage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be exceptional. I feel that you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.39,0:09:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to find a way back\Nto our world on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You say that now. but do you have an actual plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,F-For now, we'll just head back to the academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.44,0:09:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.69,0:09:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"That" What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.03,0:09:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagisa-san, it'll be fine. Things will work out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.91,0:09:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem pretty optimistic, Nanami-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan, did something good happen to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,N-N-Nothing in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say, you're really going to leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There are people in our world that we have to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.59,0:10:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Family and friends that we can't leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case. I will show you the\Nway back to Ashihara-no-kuni.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.98,0:10:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But you said there wasn't a way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I deeply apologize...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.53,0:10:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,In Nenokuni, there are eight divine\Nguardians in existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Seiryuu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.24,0:10:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Genbu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Byakko...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.52,0:10:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The other four have been captured by the\Nevil beings and must be turned back...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And under them, an inversed spell must be chanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,When the spell is used your\Nsouls can lapse through...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it will be possible to return\Nfrom Nenokuhi to Ashihara.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.56,0:10:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,God of the Sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,God of Fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Blade of Attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.94,0:10:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Spirit of Reverence...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Spirit of Sufficiency...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:10:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Spirit of the Inexplicable...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Spirit of Assurance...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Appendage of crustacean...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Appendage of insect...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Appendage of offering...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.83,0:11:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Trembling waves swaying and parting...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,These guardians can sure pick\Nthe creepiest places to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.42,0:11:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Amaterasu said that this place has been\Noccupied by evil spirits for many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I just feel that we'll run into tons\Nof problems down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so we can go back to our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.14,0:11:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.31,0:11:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when an evil spirit or whatever should\Ncome out, just let me take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Amaterasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Amaterasu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.79,0:11:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.41,0:11:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't have you risk yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.79,0:11:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We just want to go back to our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:12:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The spell requires a connection with Nenokuni.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And to be frank, I have resolved\Nin my very soul to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I truly believe that you are the kyuuseishu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So please allow me to go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.77,0:12:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru, let's bring her along.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know what's out there in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think she's leaving either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.15,0:12:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we should take her with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.03,0:12:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayaka-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.37,0:12:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like in the legend...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.29,0:12:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Four people and their leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.12,0:12:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I never said that I was involved\Nwith Hikaru in any way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, just some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.77,0:12:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagisa, don't yell out like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:12:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:12:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That scared me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You can never keep your mouth shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.95,0:13:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I sense an evil presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan, Ayaka-san, get behind me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.89,0:13:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.68,0:13:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.11,0:13:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't breathe...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what you look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.67,0:13:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You sneak...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill... Kill... I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.27,0:14:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.61,0:14:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Nanami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.99,0:14:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.04,0:14:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-san, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.37,0:14:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinatsu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.21,0:14:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Chinatsu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here of all places?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinatsu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Nanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We were friends back...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:14:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinatsu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru-san! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.71,0:15:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinatsu-chan. what happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.55,0:15:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you forget about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing is a vengeful ghost from Yomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.05,0:15:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Vengeful ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.31,0:15:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She died in her past life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.93,0:15:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel great resentment from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinatsu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming, stand aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.24,0:15:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's building power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My blade will tear it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill! Kill! Kill! Kill them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.58,0:15:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.63,0:16:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't hurt Chinatsu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.26,0:16:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.47,0:16:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinatsu-chan isn't a vengeful ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not a fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.19,0:16:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to put her to rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my friend!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, she's my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.07,0:16:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru-sama! Nagisa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.29,0:16:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Nanami-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.51,0:16:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,\NShe isn't alive anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.51,0:16:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Once an evil being, humans cannot be turned back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.97,0:16:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.51,0:16:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That monster was your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:16:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.27,0:17:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean Chinatsu-chan from back then...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.90,0:17:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinatsu-chan was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.33,0:17:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...that she was suffering so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't have anyone, and was all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I never noticed...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.69,0:17:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That Chinatsu-chan was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...picked on so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This way should lead us to Seiryuu's sacred alter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.85,0:18:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Chinatsu-chan's... diary?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would that be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan, I really don't\Nthink you should read that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Nanami-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.04,0:18:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, let me have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.83,0:18:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:18:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs16}June 10th\NMy textbook was painted black\NI won't be able to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:18:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,June 10th...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My textbooks were painted black
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.56,0:19:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I won't be able to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs16}June 29th\NSomeone put mud in my lunch.\NI haven't eaten anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,June 29th...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.56,0:19:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone put mud in my lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.32,0:19:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't been able to eat anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.41,0:19:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.83,0:19:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,July 2nd...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.37,0:19:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was in the bathroom\NI got water sprayed over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.75,0:19:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,As I tried to dry off, I could\Nhear those girls laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,July 4th...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.63,0:19:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a high fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.93,0:19:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan made me feel a little better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.72,0:19:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I would be over it by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a call that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.77,0:19:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It was from the people that surrounded me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.53,0:19:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She has a pretty damn good body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Her tits are even getting hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,July 10th...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to tell Nanami-chan about\Nall this, but decided not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All I want is for this to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.13,0:20:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything, just make it stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No? Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy shit, she's wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,July 18 th...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.18,0:20:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,While taking a break after Wednesday's class...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.14,0:20:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The girls put semen in my desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.98,0:20:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And of all things, I found it\Nwas from someone I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.03,0:20:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,NO!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:20:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.47,0:21:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No... No more...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.32,0:21:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.82,0:21:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No more...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.05,0:21:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinatsu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.77,0:22:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I will kill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.95,0:22:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Amaterasu-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.70,0:22:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,if we don't kill her, we can't get through.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.91,0:22:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is It alright with you if you can't go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.71,0:22:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She does have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.22,0:22:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.14,0:22:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.81,0:22:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.98,0:22:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If she can get through to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.73,0:22:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.86,0:22:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a vengeful ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.11,0:22:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinatsu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.57,0:22:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Nanami...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.32,0:22:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-san! Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.74,0:22:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.37,0:22:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.45,0:22:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You know who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.33,0:22:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.20,0:22:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.09,0:23:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinatsu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.46,0:23:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone... Everyone's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.93,0:23:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, stop it, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.05,0:23:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinatsu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.30,0:23:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't the only one in pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.68,0:23:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea how much Nanami-chan's\Nbeen crying and suffering?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.44,0:23:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You.. You... You...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.15,0:23:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.69,0:23:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Alive, alive, alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.83,0:23:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.91,0:23:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.04,0:23:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.96,0:23:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.17,0:23:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.88,0:23:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinatsu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.88,0:23:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.86,0:24:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... Why does everyone have to torment me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.74,0:24:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not working...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.12,0:24:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.37,0:24:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.54,0:24:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Chinatsu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.92,0:24:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinatsu-chan... let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.75,0:24:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Anywhere. I'll go with you wherever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.26,0:24:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you were sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.01,0:24:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you were alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.72,0:24:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You went through so many unbelievable things....
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.56,0:24:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone took advantage of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.19,0:24:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You fought it for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.81,0:24:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.90,0:24:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll always be here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.82,0:24:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never let go of your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.86,0:24:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.78,0:24:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, because... we're best friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.37,0:24:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.25,0:25:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.17,0:25:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinatsu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.09,0:25:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.63,0:25:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.14,0:25:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,To think a vengeful ghost could\Npass on as a heavenly spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.40,0:25:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Your servant failed, Tsukuyomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.66,0:25:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You sent Satori?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.87,0:25:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's really the best you can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.20,0:25:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Then maybe you do belong in the gutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.33,0:25:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If I may...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.17,0:25:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.04,0:25:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have another way to defeat our enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.46,0:25:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you give me another chance, I'll definitely...!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.22,0:25:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely lose, you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.35,0:26:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, Satori.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.56,0:26:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't you dare lose again.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.56,0:26:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukuyomi-sama... Thank you\Nfor this second chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.52,0:26:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be the last one I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.69,0:26:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be prepared for the consequences...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.15,0:26:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. None of them will leave.
